name: (1->4)-alpha-D-glucan 1-alpha-D-glucosylmutase
comment: The enzyme from Arthrobacter sp., Sulfolobus acidocaldarius acts on (1->4)-alpha-D-glucans containing three or more (1->4)-alpha-linked D-glucose units. Not active towards maltose.
